quran[23]{c,v,t}:
  3,52,"Tuma nde Iisaa so'unoo keeferaaku ngun e ma…ď…ďe, o maaki: \"Ko hommbo wallata lam e [diina] Alla [kan]?\". HawaaruyaŇčko en wi'i: \"Menen ko men walloo…ďe [e diina] Alla [kan], men gom…óinii Alla, seedo wonnde ko men jebbiilii…ďe"
  3,53,"Joomi amen, men gom…óinii ko Jipin…óaa Kon, men jokkii Nulaa…óo on, Winndu men e seedii…ďe …ďen"
  3,54,∆Āe fewji Alla Kadi Fewji. Ko Alla ∆Āuri Mo∆ī∆īude e fewjoo…ďe …ďen
  3,55,"Nde Alla Daalunoo: \"Hey Iisaa, Min ko mi Hunnoowo ma e ∆Āamtoowo ma faade ka Am, e La…ď…ďinoowo ma immorde e …ďen yeddu…ďe, e Wa…óa …ďen jokku…ďe ma e hoore …ďen yeddu…ďe haa √Ďalnde Darngal. Refti ko faade ka Am woni ruttorde mon, Mi √Ďaawa hakkunde mon ko luutondirayno-…óon e muu…óum"
  3,56,"Ammaa …ďen yeddu…ďe, Mi Lepta …ďen …óon lepte muusu…óe ka aduna e ka laakara, alanaa…ďe faabotoo…ďe"
  3,57,"Ammaa …ďen gom…óim…ďe …ďe golli golle-mo∆ī∆īe, O Hunnanay …ďe mbarjaari ma…ď…ďe ndin. Alla Yi…óaa too√Īoo…ďe …ďen"
  3,58,"∆äum …óoo, Me…óen Janngana maa …óum, immorde e Aayeeje e JaŇčtoore √Ďe√Ī√Īaannde"
  3,59,"Pellet, sifa Iisaa ka Alla, ko sifa Aadama; O Tagii mo immorde e mbummbuldi, refti O Daalani mo: \"Laato!\" o laatii"
  3,60,"Goonga kan ko ko immori ko Joomi maa, wata a laatodu e …ďen sikkitii…ďe"
  3,61,"Kala wennju…óo ma fii makko …ďaawo kon ko ar e maa e ganndal, maaku: \"Aree nodden …ďi…ó…ďe amen e …ďi…ó…ďe mo'on, e rew…ďe amen e rew…ďe mo'on, e ko'e amen e ko'e mo'on, refti √Īaago…óen wa…óen kuddi Alla ndin e hoore fenoo…ďe …ďen"
  3,62,"Pellet …óum …óoo, ko …óum woni fillayee goonga. Alaa rewetee…óo si wanaa Alla, pellet, Alla ko KaŇčko Woni Foolu…óo √Ďee√Īu…óo"
  3,63,"Si …ďe huccitii, pellet Alla ko Anndu…óo bonnoo…ďe …ďen"
  3,64,"Maaku: \"Hey yim…ďe Defte, aree faade e konngol fotayngol hakkunde amen e mo'on : wonnde en rewataa si wanaa Alla, en kafidataa Mo e huunde, wata yoga e me'en jogito yoga joomiraa…ďe ko woori Alla\". Si …ďe huccitii, wi'ee: \"Seeditee wonnde menen ko men jebbilii…ďe"
  3,65,"Hey yim…ďe Defte, ko wennjaŇčton fii Ibraahiima, Tawreeta e Linnjiila Jippinaaka si wanaa …ďaawo makko : e on haqqiltaa"
  3,66,"Hey ko onon …ďee, on wennjii kon ko anndal woodani on e mu'un, ko wennjaŇčton ko anndal alanaa on e mu'un? Alla no Anndi onon on anndaa"
  3,67,"Ibraahiima laatanooki AlyahuudiŇčke wanaa Annasaaraajo, si ko woni, o laatinoke oo√Īii…óo [e kala diina] jebbilanii…óo [Diina Lislaamu], o laatanooki jeyaa…óo e shirkoo…ďe …ďen"
  3,68,"Pellet, ko …ďuri hanndude e Ibraahiima e yim…ďe …ďen : ko …ďen jokku…ďe mo, e oo Annabiijo, e …ďen gom…óim…ďe. Alla ko Gi…óo gom…óim…ďe …ďen"
  3,69,"Fedde goo e yim…ďe Defte …ďen yelike nde …ďe majjina on, …ďe majjiŇčtaa si wanaa ko'e ma…ď…ďe …óen …ďe so'aa anndude"
  3,70,"Hey mon yim…ďe Defte, e ko yeddaŇčton Aayeeje Alla ∆äen hara onon ko on seedii…ďe"
  3,71,"Hey mon yim…ďe Defte, e ko jillaŇčton goonga kan e meh-re nden hi…óon suu…óa goonga kan hara onon hi…óon anndi"
  3,72,"Fedde goo jeyaande e yim…ďe Defte …ďen wi'i: \"Gom…óinee ko jippinaa kon e …ďen gom…óim…ďe ka arannde √Īallal, yeddon ka sakkitoode mayre, bela jo'o, …ďe ruttoo"
  3,73,"Wata on gom…óin si wanaa on jokku…óo diina mon kan\". Maaku: \"Pellet, ko Peewal Alla ngal woni Peewal\". [Ko kulil fii ] wata go…ó…óo goo okke sugu ko okka…óon kon maa …ďe wennjiroya on …óum ko Joomi mon. Maaku: \"Pellet …ďural ngal ko e Junngo Alla woni, Himo Ye…óa ngal on Mo O Muuyi\". Alla ko yaaju…óo […ďural] Anndu…óo"
  3,74,Himo Hertinana Yurmeende Makko nden on Mo O muuyi. Alla ko Jom ∆Āural Mawngal